contact photos for people,

00:16:56.149 --> 00:16:57.851
and larger icons for apps,

00:16:57.885 --> 00:17:00.254
making them even easier
to identify.

00:17:00.287 --> 00:17:03.257
Notifications are useful,
though they can pile up

00:17:03.290 --> 00:17:04.591
throughout the course of a day,

00:17:04.625 --> 00:17:06.393
breaking your focus
in those moments

00:17:06.426 --> 00:17:08.495
when you're trying
to get in the zone.

