while some notifications

00:17:10.797 --> 00:17:12.633
require your
immediate attention,

00:17:12.666 --> 00:17:14.601
others could be
dealt with later.

00:17:14.635 --> 00:17:16.770
To help you engage
on your own time,

00:17:16.803 --> 00:17:19.973
we're introducing
the notification summary,

00:17:20.007 --> 00:17:22.576
a helpful collection
of your notifications

00:17:22.609 --> 00:17:25.445
you can schedule to be delivered
at any time you choose,

00:17:25.479 --> 00:17:27.147
like in the morning and evening.

00:17:27.181 --> 00:17:29.249
We use on-device intelligence

00:17:29.283 --> 00:17:31.051
based on how you interact
with your apps

00:17:31.084 --> 00:17:32.386
to arrange the summary

00:17:32.419 --> 00:17:34.388
so it's easy
to quickly catch up.

00:17:35.155 --> 00:17:37.691
Notifications in the summary
are ordered by priority,

00:17:37.724 --> 00:17:40.527
with the most relevant ones
rising to the top.

00:17:40.561 --> 00:17:43.063
Notifications from people will
not end up in the summary,

00:17:43.096 --> 00:17:46.133
so you won't miss important
messages as they come in.

00:17:46.166 --> 00:17:49.002
If now really isn't a good time,

00:17:49.036 --> 00:17:52.639
