00:17:57.444 --> 00:17:59.379
so we created an easy way

00:17:59.413 --> 00:18:02.115
to signal to others
when you're doing that.

00:18:02.149 --> 00:18:04.484
Now when you're using
Do Not Disturb,

00:18:04.518 --> 00:18:07.754
