there's a way to get through.

00:18:17.364 --> 00:18:19.266
While an important part
of finding focus

00:18:19.299 --> 00:18:21.735
is about reducing distraction
from others,

00:18:21.768 --> 00:18:25.739
it's also about drawing
boundaries for yourself.

00:18:25.772 --> 00:18:27.341
There may be periods in your day

00:18:27.374 --> 00:18:30.110
when you want to be
totally focused on work,

00:18:30.143 --> 00:18:31.712
