00:59:58.098 --> 00:59:59.766
beautiful Cupertino weather.

00:59:59.800 --> 01:00:01.835
And it was just one of those
moments where it dawned on us

00:59:59.800 --> 01:00:01.835
And it was just one of those
moments where it dawned on us

01:00:01.869 --> 01:00:03.737
that Corrie app was going
to have an impact

01:00:03.770 --> 01:00:05.973
on so many people’s hearts
