01:09:01.942 --> 01:09:03.510
This is a vital sign
that measures

01:09:03.544 --> 01:09:04.912
how many breaths
you take per minute.

01:09:04.945 --> 01:09:06.880
And since your sleeping
respiratory rate

01:09:06.914 --> 01:09:08.782
tends to be consistent
over time,

01:09:08.815 --> 01:09:11.485
a change may indicate a shift
in your overall wellness.

01:09:11.518 --> 01:09:13.854
You'll be notified
if a meaningful trend

01:09:13.887 --> 01:09:16.290
in your respiratory rate
has been identified.

01:09:16.323 --> 01:09:18.025
And you can see
even more details

01:09:18.058 --> 01:09:20.160
in Respiratory Rate
in the Health app.

